# AR Instrument Studio Walkthrough (Synthesia Mode)

## Summary
Complete AR Studio with **Falling Notes** and **Real Audio Mapping**.

## Visuals (Synthesia Style)
-   **Falling Blocks**: Notes fall from the top of the screen.
-   **Target Zone**: Bottom line where you should strike.
-   **Score**: +10 points for hitting the correct finger at the right time.

## Audio Map
-   **Left Hand**: C1, D1, E1, F1, G1.
-   **Right Hand**: A1, B1, C1, D1, E1.
-   **Sharps**: Curl your finger to play Sharp (e.g. [c1s.wav](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/sounds/c1s.wav)).

## Controls
-   **Strike**: Downward Motion (>0.02).
-   **Reset**: Lift finger up.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run ar_studio.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
